channel.title: Economic Indicators - New items on govinfo
channel.description: Provides access to newly published GovInfo content from the Economic Indicators. Available from April 1995 forward, this monthly publication is prepared by the Council of Economic Advisers for the Joint Economic Committee. It provides economic information on gross domestic product, income, employment, production, business activity, prices, money, credit, security markets, Federal finance, and international statistics.

image.title: Economic Indicators - New items on govinfo

channel.copyright: Title 17, Section 105, United States Code, provides that: Copyright protection under this title is not available for any work of the United States Government, but the United States Government is not precluded from receiving and holding copyrights transferred to it by assignment, bequest, or otherwise. For more information, see https://www.govinfo.gov/about/policies#copyright
